flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Material receipt notification from SAP S/4HANA.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawler - Receive material receipt notification]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Process Builder - Prioritize and stage incoming materials]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Process Builder - Determine line-side replenishment timing and sequence]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: Process Builder - Group components into kits or perform minor sub-assemblies]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: Process Builder - Adjust inventory accuracy targets and cycle counting frequency]
  N5 --> N6[Cortex: Process Builder - Route empty containers for efficient return logistics]
  N6 --> N7[Cortex: Process Builder - Identify and escalate material shortages]
  N7 --> N8{Decision: Determine optimal actions for material receiving, line-side replenishment, internal parts kitting, inventory accuracy, empty container management, and material shortage identification.}
  N7 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, improved material flow, minimized stockouts, faster material turnaround, enhanced OTIF, and better working capital efficiency.]
  N8 -->|Insufficient inventory levels detected| B1[Escalate to procurement team]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Expedite orders or alternate sourcing]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N8 -->|Critical material shortage identified| B2[Re-sequence production]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Prevent production stops]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N8 -->|High inventory accuracy variance| B3[Increase cycle counting frequency]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Improve inventory accuracy]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]